    "And Rehoboam went to Shechem: for to Shechem were all <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> come to make him king.",
    "And it came to pass, when Jeroboam the son of Nebat, who was in <span class=\"place\">Egypt</span>, whither he had fled from the presence of <span class=\"person\">Solomon</span> the king, heard it, that Jeroboam returned out of <span class=\"place\">Egypt</span>.",
