    "And <span class=\"person\">Asa</span> had an army of men that bare targets and spears, out of <span class=\"person\">Judah</span> three hundred thousand; and out of <span class=\"person\">Benjamin</span>, that bare shields and drew bows, two hundred and fourscore thousand: all these were mighty men of valour.",
