    "But there came a man of God to him, saying, O king, let not the army of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> go with thee; for the LORD is not with <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>, to wit, with all the children of <span class=\"person\">Ephraim</span>.",
    "But if thou wilt go, do it, be strong for the battle: God shall make thee fall before the enemy: for God hath power to help, and to cast down.",
