    "Then Amaziah separated them, to wit, the army that was come to him out of <span class=\"person\">Ephraim</span>, to go home again: wherefore their anger was greatly kindled against <span class=\"person\">Judah</span>, and they returned home in great anger.",
    "And Amaziah strengthened himself, and led forth his people, and went to the valley of salt, and smote of the children of <span class=\"place\">Seir</span> ten thousand.",
