    "But the soldiers of the army which Amaziah sent back, that they should not go with him to battle, fell upon the cities of <span class=\"person\">Judah</span>, from <span class=\"place\">Samaria</span> even unto Bethhoron, and smote three thousand of them, and took much spoil.",
