    "And afterward they made ready for themselves, and for the priests: because the priests the sons of <span class=\"person\">Aaron</span> were busied in offering of burnt offerings and the fat until night; therefore the Levites prepared for themselves, and for the priests the sons of <span class=\"person\">Aaron</span>.",
    "And the singers the sons of Asaph were in their place, according to the commandment of <span class=\"person\">David</span>, and Asaph, and Heman, and Jeduthun the king's seer; and the porters waited at every gate; they might not depart from their service; for their brethren the Levites prepared for them.",
