    "In the eighteenth year of the reign of Josiah was this passover kept.",
    "After all this, when Josiah had prepared the temple, Necho king of <span class=\"place\">Egypt</span> came up to fight against Carchemish by <span class=\"place\">Euphrates</span>: and Josiah went out against him.",
