    "And <span class=\"person\">Jeremiah</span> lamented for Josiah: and all the singing men and the singing women spake of Josiah in their lamentations to this day, and made them an ordinance in <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>: and, behold, they are written in the lamentations.",
